{"tid":1572550,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"咩「爽完聽日要繼續」個啲我屌你老母","createTime":"2019-09-15T16:59:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T17:20:07.000Z","uid":226573,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b614dd59298330a0128c514a846f84065c4e4897","tid":1572550,"uid":226573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:59:07.000Z","msg":"個個淨係重覆post個幾條打福建佬片，得一半頭破血流<br />\n<br />\n爽？開心？9百幾位被捕人士呢？個個未返狗屋就已經頭破血流，未講入到去嘅精神虐待、新屋嶺骨折、被告嘅工作案底前途，更加未講9位義士、831 3位手足生死未卜、呢幾日咁多單「無可疑」「自殺」案<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母，唔好打左幾個藍絲廢老一陣咁小事就開心得咁早好冇，完全同黑警對待手足嘅行為同數字都唔對等呀，咁就開心，你地對唔對得住傷痕累累嘅被捕人士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請去聲緩聽日提堂嘅手足/繼續關注「自殺」案、831、被捕義士，同幫推有用post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4d0177da76d964f392eb80c7be5807ebf9cd14d","tid":1572550,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T17:06:42.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n[品葱轉載] [文宣戰術] 教你如何宣傳反共，緊貼現在熱門事件。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ebhFbS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ebhFbS</a>"},{"pid":"6735ad43191244cce4bf4873d0f3a071c39837f9","tid":1572550,"uid":226573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T17:07:12.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"6ee7942d8848b71c149581ec3060625db0c8e69d","tid":1572550,"uid":226573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T17:07:24.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"4ea0dce60a38c6d4b91f811f59b4c5238587ca0c","tid":1572550,"uid":287112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T17:07:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"33a1ffbe93b665fd5a4a813c550f825d6f3c20ef","tid":1572550,"uid":226573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T17:08:38.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"2bee7d6d7e17b503122ae161e56cebb485de6f43","tid":1572550,"uid"